com.yworks.yfiles.graphml

Class CreationProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.graphml.CreationProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMapper<Object,Object>

    public class CreationProperties
extends Object
implements IMapper<Object,Object>
    A simple mutable implementation of IMapper that is typed for Object keys and values.

    This class is used by the GraphMLParser to store properties of an item before it has been created. An instance of this class can be found in the ILookup.lookup(java.lang.Class) of the IParseContext during the parsing of an item. Custom parsers may populate the dictionary with various properties that can then be used by the IGraphElementFactory during the creation of the item.

    See Also:
    IGraphElementFactory, GraphMLParser
